title: Car Sliding Door Contact Switch Compatible with VW T3 T4 T5
features: These are a perfect replacement for the VW T4 please look at how many pins you have before you purchase.
Used to install central locking motors in sliding van doors.
Universal fit Sliding door contact designed to easily get power to the door lock actuators mounted in the sliding door on vans.
They are designed to be mounted on the door frame area of the sliding door and also be used in the rear door of the van.
Among them, to limit the use of space in the door frame to prevent the run line into the door frame.
